freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Had a really bad headache yesterday.  Could not relate it to anything really. Better today.
Have a lump above my left clavicle.  Same side as vaccine.
Have an inflammed lymph node above left clavicle same side as vaccine.
My joints are aching more than normal. Seem to be really stiff. Aching is slowing increasing in intensity.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: My arm swelled up from injection site down to my wrist.
These symptoms seem to come and go not sure it they are related.
Will the vaccine work if injected SQ rather than IM?
